    Creates an array from string `$args`.
-   Uses global: (`object`)
    [`$wpdb`](/Class_Reference/wpdb "Class Reference/wpdb")

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.3.0

Source File
-----------

`get_objects_in_term()` is located in `/wp-includes/taxonomy.php`.

